    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Add flag that will make cython output a rule suitable for make describing the dependencies of the main source file.\n\nlike this:\n\n```\n$ cython -M foo.pxd\n\nfoo.c: bar.pxd\n```\n\nMigrated from http://trac.cython.org/ticket/655\n",
